"uploads/8283bd09-8805-4070-934e-03675d6f5835.jpg)"
msgstr ""
"![Timber trail at Pureoa Forest Park](/assets/"
"uploads/8283bd09-8805-4070-934e-03675d6f5835.jpg)"

